<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Theme Management - Scriptorium Web UI</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 20px; }
    .error { color: red; background: #ffe6e6; padding: 10px; margin: 10px 0; }
    .message { color: green; background: #e6ffe6; padding: 10px; margin: 10px 0; }
    .suggestion { color: #666; font-style: italic; }
    table { border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; margin: 10px 0; }
    th, td { border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px; text-align: left; }
    th { background-color: #f2f2f2; }
    .button { background: #007cba; color: white; padding: 5px 10px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 3px; border: none; cursor: pointer; }
    .button:hover { background: #005a87; }
    .button.danger { background: #dc3545; }
    .button.danger:hover { background: #c82333; }
    .section { margin: 20px 0; }
    .section h3 { margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .theme-type { font-weight: bold; }
    .system-theme { color: #6c757d; }
    .user-theme { color: #28a745; }
    .clone-form { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 15px 0; }
    .clone-form input, .clone-form select { margin: 5px; padding: 5px; }
    .clone-form label { display: inline-block; width: 120px; font-weight: bold; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Theme Management</h1>
  
  <a href="/" class="button">‚Üê Back to Dashboard</a>
  
  <% if @error %>
    <div class="error">
      <strong>Error:</strong> <%= @error %>
      <% if @suggestion %>
        <div class="suggestion"><%= @suggestion %></div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  <% end %>
  
  <% if @message %>
    <div class="message"><%= @message %></div>
  <% end %>

  <div class="section">
    <h3>Available Themes</h3>
    
    <% if @themes && !@themes.empty? %>
      <table>
        <tr>
          <th>Theme Name</th>
          <th>Type</th>
          <th>Actions</th>
        </tr>
        <% @themes.each do |theme| %>
          <tr>
            <td class="theme-type"><%= theme %></td>
            <td>
              <% if @system_themes.include?(theme) %>
                <span class="system-theme">System Theme</span>
              <% elsif @user_themes.include?(theme) %>
                <span class="user-theme">User Theme</span>
              <% else %>
                <span>Unknown</span>
              <% end %>
            </td>
            <td>
              <a href="/edit_theme/<%= theme %>" class="button" style="margin-right: 5px; text-decoration: none;">Edit</a>
              <% if @user_themes.include?(theme) %>
                <form method="post" action="/theme_management/delete" style="display: inline;" onsubmit="return confirm('Are you sure you want to delete theme \'<%= theme %>\'? This action cannot be undone.');">
                  <input type="hidden" name="theme_name" value="<%= theme %>">
                  <button type="submit" class="button danger">Delete</button>
                </form>
              <% else %>
                <span style="color: #6c757d;">System themes cannot be deleted</span>
              <% end %>
            </td>
          </tr>
        <% end %>
      </table>
    <% else %>
      <p>No themes found.</p>
    <% end %>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h3>Clone Theme</h3>
    <p>Create a new theme by cloning an existing one. You can then edit the cloned theme's files to customize it.</p>
    
    <div class="clone-form">
      <form method="post" action="/theme_management/clone">
        <div>
          <label for="source_theme">Source Theme:</label>
          <select name="source_theme" id="source_theme" required>
            <option value="">Select a theme to clone...</option>
            <% @themes.each do |theme| %>
              <option value="<%= theme %>"><%= theme %> (<%= @system_themes.include?(theme) ? 'System' : 'User' %>)</option>
            <% end %>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div>
          <label for="new_name">New Theme Name:</label>
          <input type="text" name="new_name" id="new_name" placeholder="my-custom-theme" required pattern="[a-zA-Z0-9_-]+" title="Only letters, numbers, hyphens, and underscores allowed">
        </div>
        <div>
          <button type="submit" class="button">Clone Theme</button>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h3>Editing Themes</h3>
    <p>After cloning a theme, you can edit its files using the file editing functionality. Theme files are located in:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>System themes:</strong> <code>themes/&lt;theme-name&gt;/</code></li>
      <li><strong>User themes:</strong> <code>themes/&lt;theme-name&gt;/</code></li>
    </ul>
    <p>Common theme files include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><code>layout.txt</code> - Main layout configuration</li>
      <li><code>header.txt</code> - Header content</li>
      <li><code>footer.txt</code> - Footer content</li>
      <li><code>left.txt</code> - Left sidebar content</li>
      <li><code>right.txt</code> - Right sidebar content</li>
      <li><code>main.txt</code> - Main content area</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
